</listitem><listitem><para>Q0 peak position which is related to the d-spacing as q0 = 2pi/d (e.g., 0.01)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>M I(Q)=I0/(1+(|q-q0|*xi)^m)^p (e.g., 2)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>P I(Q)=I0/(1+(|q-q0|*xi)^m)^p (e.g., 2) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
